Subject:  Non  paper airplane.

Procedure:  A Foundation member launches a non  paper airplane while a nearby Foundation member activates his Zune brand cellphone during its take-off.

Results:  Subject clocked at 39,000m/s releasing energy equivalent to ██ kT of TNT.

Follow-Up:  Foundation forces were successful in covering up the incident and avoiding a third world war.
